💰 deposit flow

```text id="dep_flow"
1. find account
2. validate account ACTIVE
3. create com.digitalbank.entity.Transaction (DEPOSIT)
4. increase balance
5. save
```

---

💸 withdraw flow

```text id="wd_flow"
1. find account
2. check com.digitalbank.entity.Status ACTIVE
3. check balance >= amount
4. create com.digitalbank.entity.Transaction (WITHDRAW)
5. decrease balance
6. save
```

---

 🔁 transfer flow (VERY IMPORTANT)

```text id="tr_flow"
1. find sender account
2. find receiver account
3. check sender balance
4. create referenceId (TX-123)
5. create WITHDRAW transaction (sender)
6. create DEPOSIT transaction (receiver)
7. update both balances
8. save everything
```

---

