# ⚠️ 4. Important Cascade Rules (Banking-safe)

DO NOT overuse cascade in banking.

### Recommended:

* ❌ No Cascade ALL for transactions
* ✔ Only controlled saving via Service layer

Reason:
👉 Banks never delete accounts and transactions together automatically

---

